snippet: Visitors swarmed the 20 food tents of the Queens International Night Market on the first of 16 scheduled evenings of its first year.
abstract: Queens International Night Market, featuring more than 100 vendors selling diverse range of authentic ethnic foods and products, officially opens; 16 events are scheduled throughout the year, in parking lot outside the New York Hall of Science at Flushing Meadows-Corona Park.
lead_paragraph: Visitors swarmed the 20 food tents of the Queens International Night Market on the first of 16 scheduled evenings of its first year.

headline.main: Squid Sticks After Dark at the Queens International Night Market
